            corresponds to the edition <bibl>
                  <ptr target="bm:Grebaut1935Eqabani"/>
               </bibl>, while <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4663Eqabanni"/> contains an additional
            section which narrates how a nobleman in the city of Franks (<foreign xml:lang="gez">ʾafrengi</foreign>) received
               the prayer from heaven. The general record to be used in cases where the recension is not known is 
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT6279EqabanniGen"/>.</p>
